<p>JCS, from <a href="http://irreal.org/blog">Irreal</a>, recently <a href="http://irreal.org/blog/?p%3D4777">highlighted</a> fuco's <a href="https://github.com/Fuco1/dired-hacks">dired-hacks</a>. <a href="https://github.com/Fuco1/dired-hacks/blob/master/dired-subtree.el">dired-subtree</a> is super handy for drilling subdirectories down. Bound &lt;tab&gt; and &lt;backtab&gt; to toggle and cycle subtrees.</p>
<pre><code class="language-{.commonlisp">(use-package dired-subtree :ensure t
  :after dired
  :config
  (bind-key &quot;&lt;tab&gt;&quot; #'dired-subtree-toggle dired-mode-map)
  (bind-key &quot;&lt;backtab&gt;&quot; #'dired-subtree-cycle dired-mode-map))
</code></pre>
